#### How to use

Check the [Read Me](https://github.com/nadundesilva/mesh-manager/tree/{{VERSION_TAG}}#how-to-use) for instructions on how to use the Operator.

#### Changelog:

- Add support for creating deployment from pod spec
- Add support for creating service automatically from pod spec ports
- Prevent resource creation when resources are missing
- Add support for creating network policy to limit incoming traffic only from dependents
- Add events and status for improving debuggability
- Add finalier to prevent deletion when there are dependents are present
